          "_name": "features12",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"features12\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    \n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Icons\" name=\"showIcons\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Media Size\" name=\"mediaSize\" min=\"10\" max=\"60\" step=\"1\" value=\"49\">\n        <select title=\"Cards\" name=\"cardsAmount\">\n            <option value=\"2\">2</option>\n            <option value=\"4\" selected>4</option>\n        </select>\n\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Background Image\" value=\"../_images/background2.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" value=\"#f9f9f9\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Background Video\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uNCr7NdOJgw\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" checked condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title pb-2 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n            Poster Presentation</h2>\n        <h3 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n            Click any text or icon to edit or style it. Use the block parameters to hide/show text or icons and change media size.\n        </h3>\n\n        <div class=\"media-container-row pt-5\">\n            <div class=\"block-content align-right\">\n                <div class=\"card pl-3 pr-3 pb-5\">\n                    <div class=\"mbr-card-img-title\">\n                        <div class=\"card-img pb-3\" mbr-if=\"showIcons\">\n                             <span mbr-icon class=\"mbri-upload mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"mbr-crt-title\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title py-2 mbr-crt-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-crt-title\">Abstract</h4>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>                \n\n                    <div class=\"card-box\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-section-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-text\"><a href=\"https://www.isbnpa.org/files/annual_meetings/2019/07/11/22/attachments/5d277dbf5f214.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">ISBNPA Abstract Book</a></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"card pl-3 pr-3 pb-5\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount > 2\">\n                    <div class=\"mbr-card-img-title\">\n                        <div class=\"card-img pb-3\" mbr-if=\"showIcons\">\n                            <span mbr-icon class=\"mbri-drag-n-drop2 mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"mbr-crt-title\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title py-2 mbr-crt-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-crt-title\">Creating a Chord Diagram</h4>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"card-box\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-section-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-text\">I had a few quesitons about how to create the chord diagram on my poster. Chord diagrams come from the field of genetics and show relationships between vairables. The thicker the line, in the case of the systematic review, the more times the two vriables have been investigated together in the literature. <br><a href=\"https://flourish.studio/2018/07/25/how-to-make-a-chord-diagram/\" target=\"_blank\">Tutorial</a></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-figure\" mbr-style=\"{'width': mediaSize + '%'}\">\n                <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/isbnpa-poster-429x603.png\" alt=\"Mobirise\" title>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"block-content align-left  \">\n                <div class=\"card pl-3 pr-3 pb-5\">\n                    <div class=\"mbr-card-img-title\">\n                        <div class=\"card-img pb-3\" mbr-if=\"showIcons\">\n                             <span mbr-icon class=\"mbri-features mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"mbr-crt-title\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title py-2 mbr-crt-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-crt-title\">Full Systematic Review Protocol</h4>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>                \n\n                    <div class=\"card-box\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-section-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-text\">The full review protocol is pubished on Prospero&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.crd.york.ac.uk/prospero/display_record.php?RecordID=87274\" target=\"_blank\">CRD42018087274</a> </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"card pl-3 pr-3 pb-5\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount > 2\">\n                    <div class=\"mbr-card-img-title\">\n                        <div class=\"card-img pb-3\" mbr-if=\"showIcons\">\n                            <span mbr-icon class=\"mbri-sites mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"mbr-crt-title\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title py-2 mbr-crt-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-crt-title\">View the poster here on <a href=\"https://speakerdeck.com/francescapontin/isbnpa-poster\" target=\"_blank\">Speakerdeck</a></h4>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"card-box\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-section-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-text\"><script async class=\"speakerdeck-embed\" data-id=\"c12258f1dc7141f5ab9a44217f306de8\" data-ratio=\"0.707182320441989\" src=\"//speakerdeck.com/assets/embed.js\"></script><script async class=\"speakerdeck-embed\" data-id=\"c12258f1dc7141f5ab9a44217f306de8\" data-ratio=\"0.707182320441989\" src=\"//speakerdeck.com/assets/embed.js\"></script></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "rxJ0lkBgNN",
